OL,4,Chuman rights obligations, MPs and
OL,5,Cpeers warn
OL,7,FRishi Sunak's proposed Rwanda asylum
OL,8,Flaw is "fundamentally incompatible"
OL,9,Fwith the UK's human rights obligations
OL,10,Fand would flout international law, MPs
OL,11,Fand peers have warned.
OL,13,FParliament's Joint Committee on Human
OL,14,FRights said the Government's Safety of
OL,15,FRwanda (Asylum and Immigration) Bill
OL,16,F"risks untold damage" to the UK's hard-
OL,17,Fwon reputation as a proponent of human
OL,18,Frights internationally.
