OL,3,CRwanda Bill incompatible with UK's
OL,4,Chuman rights obligations, MPs and
OL,5,Cpeers warn
OL,7,FThe controversial draft legislation
OL,8,Fand a treaty with Rwanda are intended
OL,9,Fto prevent further legal challenges to
OL,10,Fthe stalled deportation scheme after a
OL,11,FSupreme Court ruling against the plan.
OL,13,FBy compelling judges to regard Rwanda
OL,14,Fas safe, ministers want to be able to
OL,15,Fsend asylum seekers on a one-way trip
OL,16,Fto the east African country.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/12
