OL,3,CRwanda Bill incompatible with UK's
OL,4,Chuman rights obligations, MPs and
OL,5,Cpeers warn
OL,7,FBut the crossbench committee of MPs
OL,8,Fand Lords said they had heard evidence
OL,9,Fthat the problems identified by the
OL,10,FSupreme Court could not be resolved so
OL,11,Fquickly.
OL,13,FThe panel said in a report: "We are
OL,14,Fnot persuaded that Parliament can be
OL,15,Fconfident that Rwanda is now safe. In
OL,16,Fany event, we consider that the courts
OL,17,Fare best placed to resolve such
OL,18,Fcontested issues of fact."
