OL,4,Chuman rights obligations, MPs and
OL,5,Cpeers warn
OL,7,FThe Bill, which is going through
OL,8,FParliament, seeks to severely limit
OL,9,Fasylum seekers' ability to appeal
OL,10,Fagainst being put on a flight to
OL,11,FKigali.
OL,13,FWhile they can try to claim Rwanda is
OL,14,Fnot safe for them as an individual,
OL,15,Fthey cannot argue that it is generally
OL,16,Funsafe or that they are at risk of
OL,17,Fbeing transferred to a third country
OL,18,Fwhere they could be in danger.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/12
