OL,4,Chuman rights obligations, MPs and
OL,5,Cpeers warn
OL,7,FThe committee said this makes the Bill
OL,8,Fincompatible with the UK's
OL,9,Finternational obligations, most
OL,10,Fobviously Article 13 of the European
OL,11,FConvention on Human Rights (ECHR) `
OL,12,Fthe right to an effective remedy.
OL,14,FThe legislation also says it is up to
OL,15,Fministers to decide whether to comply
OL,16,Fwith interim rulings issued by judges
OL,17,Fat the European Court of Human Rights,
OL,18,Fand therefore "openly invites the
OL,19,Fpossibility of the UK breaching
OL,20,Finternational law", according to the
OL,21,Freport.
