OL,7,FA so-called Rule 39 interim measure `
OL,8,Fbranded a "pyjama injunction" because
OL,9,Fit can be issued outside normal court
OL,10,Fhours ` contributed to the grounding
OL,11,Fin 2022 of the first flight that was
OL,12,Fset to carry asylum seekers to Rwanda.
OL,14,FJoint committee chairwoman Joanna
OL,15,FCherry said: "This Bill is designed to
OL,16,Fremove vital safeguards against
OL,17,Fpersecution and human rights abuses,
OL,18,Fincluding the fundamental right to
OL,19,Faccess a court. Hostility to human
OL,20,Frights is at its heart and no
OL,21,Famendments can salvage it.
