OL,7,FThe asylum scheme comes with a #290
OL,8,Fmillion bill but a series of legal
OL,9,Fchallenges has meant no flights have
OL,10,Ftaken off since it was proposed in
OL,11,F2022.
OL,13,FUnder the plan, people who cross the
OL,14,FChannel in small boats could be
OL,15,Fremoved to Rwanda rather than being
OL,16,Fallowed to seek asylum in the UK.
