OL,7,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "We
OL,8,Fare committed to tackling this major
OL,9,Fglobal challenge with bold and
OL,10,Finnovative solutions, and the Rwanda
OL,11,Fscheme is doing just that.
OL,13,F"The Bill we have introduced, and the
OL,14,Ftreaty alongside it, are the best way
OL,15,Fof getting flights off to Rwanda as
OL,16,Fsoon as possible.
